            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 5 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program. The script targets the shame loop around past money decisions: the replayed choices, the regret, the fear that old mistakes have permanently narrowed what's possible. Use it when the guilt is active, not when you're making a current decision."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
